headline.main: Alabama City to Re-enact March That Sparked 'Bloody Sunday'
headline.print_headline: Alabama City to Re-enact March That Sparked 'Bloody Sunday'

lead_paragraph: Thousands of people are expected to converge in the city of Selma, Alabama for the annual re-enactment of a key event in the civil rights movement.
